text: The European Taekwondo Championships (WT) are the European senior championships in Taekwondo, first held in Barcelona 1976.ITF is a smaller international federation unaffiliated to either WTF or IOC, and competing under slightly modified rules including the wearing of padded gloves and footwear. ==References== == Other websites == * Official site of the European Taekwondo Union Category:Taekwondo Category:Sport in Europe
title: European Taekwondo Championships
